Short:AMOS Bob/Sprite editor.
Type: dev/amos
Uploader: Brian.Lloyd@canrem.com
Author: Brian.Lloyd@canrem.com

This is a demo version of The Bob Shop a shareware
sprite/bob bank  editor for the Amos programming language.
This demo will run for  only 15 minutes at a time.  
Features include a full set of drawing tools, custom
brushes, pattern  fills, VCR type playback of sprite/bob
banks, variable zoom window and page flipping for animation
creation.